---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Playground"
  description="Playground - 小型网页试验与前端表达实验"
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-sm text-forest-600 font-medium mb-3">Playground</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-4">小型网页试验</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-600 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        这里放一些与科研主页无直接关系的小型网页试验。它们主要用于测试前端交互、视觉风格和个人表达。
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/playground/yanqi-clock/" class="block group">
        <article class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-stone-200 p-6 hover:border-forest-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all h-full">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest-50 text-forest-600 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">
              ◷
            </span>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-stone-800 group-hover:text-forest-600 transition-colors mb-2">
                雁栖湖幻想时间
              </h2>
              <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
                一个动态时钟与粒子背景的小实验，统一到本站的生态计算视觉风格。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-forest-50 text-forest-600 rounded text-xs">
              Front-end experiment
            </span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-deepblue-50 text-deepblue-600 rounded text-xs">
              Stylized clock
            </span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-12 bg-stone-100 rounded-xl p-6">
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
        <span class="font-medium text-stone-700">说明：</span>
        Playground 内容不代表科研成果，只是前端与表达方式的小实验。主页的主要重心仍然是研究记录、教程笔记和真实内容积累。
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
